WEBVTT

00:11:57.042 --> 00:12:00.500
but sometimes it requires
a deeper exploration of their values

00:12:01.583 --> 00:12:03.917
to really understand how to move forward.

00:12:05.125 --> 00:12:06.393
In a similar way,

00:12:06.417 --> 00:12:08.559
our nation is facing a crisis

00:12:08.583 --> 00:12:11.434
with the increasing number
of asylum seekers at our borders

00:12:11.458 --> 00:12:12.809
and in our communities,

00:12:12.833 --> 00:12:17.125
and it compels us to re-examine
some of our own fundamental values.

00:12:18.500 --> 00:12:22.059
What does it mean
when we value health and safety?

00:12:22.083 --> 00:12:24.042
What does it mean when we value security,

00:12:25.958 --> 00:12:28.101
life, liberty,

00:12:28.125 --> 00:12:29.809
the life of children?

00:12:29.833 --> 00:12:31.143
What about this one --